snippet.title: Diana plays with balloons in dresses of princesses
snippet.description:
Diana dresses up in princess dresses in different colors and learn colors with balloons. She is have fun under the nursery nursery for babies - Finger family song about colors. This is fun learning for kids. Learn colors with us and our song for #children:

Yellow Color, Yellow Color, where are you?
Here I am, hereI am. How do you do?

Green Color, Green Color, where are you?
Here I am, here I am. How do you do?

White Color, White Color, where are you?
Here I am, here I am. How do you do?

Red Color, Red Color, where are you?
Here I am, here I am. How do you do?

Blue #Color, Blue Color, where are you?
Here I am, here I am. How do you do?

Learn Colors for kids with #Balloons and nursery rhymes for children Finger family song
